<Folder><name>⭐ Food — regional picks</name><Placemark><name>Mesón Asador</name><description>Empordà charcoal grills, weekday menú. Good value (avoid Dalí-museum strip). https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Mes%C3%B3n%20Asador%20Figueres</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>2.9600095,42.2666767,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Can Jepet</name><description>Pyrenees mountain cooking — civet de jabalí (wild boar). TA 4.3, #1 in Setcases. (approx loc) https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Can%20Jepet%20Setcases</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>2.305,42.375,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Lo Pigal Casa Kiko</name><description>Pallars traditional — lamb, carne a la piedra. TA 4.5. Mains ~€20-30. Reserve. (approx loc) https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Lo%20Pigal%20Casa%20Kiko%20Llessui</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>1.078,42.452,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Restaurant Pessets</name><description>Mountain trout, venison, civets. Guía Repsol. Mid-value. https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Restaurant%20Pessets%20Sort</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>1.12952,42.4099754,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Bar Pirineus</name><description>Village bar, well-priced midday menú; conill guisat (rabbit stew). https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Bar%20Pirineus%20La%20Pobla%20de%20Segur</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>0.9654046,42.2421314,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Bodegas del Sobrarbe</name><description>Aragonese in 11th-c. cellar — ternasco. Menú ~€17-20. TA ~3.5 (atmosphere pick). https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Bodegas%20del%20Sobrarbe%20A%C3%ADnsa</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>0.1388952,42.4169578,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Restaurante La Parrilla</name><description>Charcoal chuletón &amp; ternasco, homestyle Pyrenean grills. Good value. https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Restaurante%20La%20Parrilla%20A%C3%ADnsa</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>0.1389017,42.4146437,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Casa Blasquico Gaby</name><description>Best table in the valley — refined Aragonese. Set ~€16. TA Travellers&#x27; Choice. Book. (approx loc) https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Casa%20Blasquico%20Gaby%20Hecho</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-0.752,42.741,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Borda Chiquín</name><description>Converted mountain borda — migas de pastor &amp; grilled meats. https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Borda%20Chiqu%C3%ADn%20Ans%C3%B3</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-0.8321405,42.8243342,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>La Cocina Aragonesa</name><description>Traditional Aragonese. Menú del día €16. Ternasco asado. https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=La%20Cocina%20Aragonesa%20Jaca</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-0.5533162,42.5695965,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Casa Tapia</name><description>Valley standout — trout with ham, Roncal DO cheese. Menú €14.50. Best in Roncal. (approx loc) https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Casa%20Tapia%20Isaba</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-0.927,42.855,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Venta de Juan Pito</name><description>Family-run traditional Roncalés cooking, local produce. https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Venta%20de%20Juan%20Pito%20Isaba</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-0.8574285,42.9379474,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Asador Kixkia</name><description>Navarrese cider-house asador — chuletón a la brasa. TA 4.2, #1 in Ochagavía. Biker stop. (approx loc) https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Asador%20Kixkia%20Ochagav%C3%ADa</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-1.088,42.908,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Restaurante Auñamendi</name><description>Cordero al chilindrón, trout. Weekday menú €16. TA 3.8. https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Restaurante%20Au%C3%B1amendi%20Ochagav%C3%ADa</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-1.0900861,42.9047152,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Borda Berri</name><description>Parte Vieja pintxos benchmark — veal cheek, rib kebab. ~€15pp. Made to order. https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Borda%20Berri%20San%20Sebasti%C3%A1n</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-1.9669562,43.2945896,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Bar Néstor</name><description>Cult bar — txuleta steak, tomato salad, one daily tortilla (ask early). https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Bar%20N%C3%A9stor%20San%20Sebasti%C3%A1n</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-1.9837014,43.3238831,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Gandarias</name><description>Reliable old-town all-rounder — Gilda, txuleta skewers, foie toast. https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Gandarias%20San%20Sebasti%C3%A1n</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-1.9857674,43.3239943,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark></Folder>
